10800:〔Ban〕“Heh, no surprise there, Momo-chan. You've always been quite the busy bee.”\p;
10900:〔Ban〕“So? Whatcha got?”\p;
11000:Momose raised her hands skyward and stretched far and wide. Tilting her head slightly to the side, a satisfying “pop!” sounded from her bones.\p;
11100:〔Momose〕“No such luck. I've already thrown in the towel.”\p;
