11600:〔Momose〕“But I'm at the end of my rope. I'm not sure if it's all extremely well hidden, or if my guess is just wrong like Suwa-chan suggested.”\p;
11700:〔Ban〕“Hmm...”\p;
11800:〔Ban〕“For times like these, there's an ironclad rule in the detective's handbook: ‘attack from a different angle.’”\p;
11900:〔Suwa〕“Sir, do you have some idea of what might be going on?”\p;
12000:Ban stopped the hand that was fanning himself, then wet his lips with his tongue.\p;
12100:〔Ban〕“Who do you think might benefit from the GE rate bein' higher on weekends?”\p;
